{"calories":"730","carbs":87,"category":{"badge_name":"","display_name":"Dinner","display_order":1,"is_filterable":false,"insight_segment_slug":"main-recipe-ratings","slug":"main"},"choices_available":[],"description":"Very few dishes are as comforting and satisfying as one of our favorite childhood classics: macaroni and cheese. Chef Laura remembers having her mom’s homemade mac and cheese, so we chose to honor this crowd-pleasing, cheesetastic dish for Mother’s Day. Here, tender fusilli pasta is coated with a rich, creamy sauce that has, count them, \u003ci\u003efour\u003c/i\u003e different types of cheese: Parmesan, Fontina, Gruyère, and Cheddar. Laura tops hers with breadcrumbs that form a crunchy crust in the oven—her mother’s favorite part of the dish! Served with a spring green salad, this mac and cheese will become a gold standard, we’re sure of it.","difficulty":"easy","external_id":"1ad37642d7","fat":27,"images":[{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/21998/2431_Four_Cheese_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Mixed_Greens___0005_1.jpg","size":"full","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/21998/menu_small_2431_Four_Cheese_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Mixed_Greens___0005_1.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"card"}},{"image":{"url":"/assets/blank_profile-62376be1ebee267193d25c20f8cd8bc5a6c47743a4a323d32a54ecdf231b7b80.png","size":"large_cropped","type":"main_cropped"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/21995/2431_Four_Cheese_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Mixed_Greens___0004_1.jpg","size":"full","type":"portrait"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/21992/2431_Four_Cheese_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Mixed_Greens___0002_1.jpg","size":"full","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/21992/hero_2431_Four_Cheese_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Mixed_Greens___0002_1.jpg","size":"hero","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/21992/menu_small_2431_Four_Cheese_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Mixed_Greens___0002_1.jpg","size":"medium-rectangle","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/21992/small_square_2431_Four_Cheese_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Mixed_Greens___0002_1.jpg","size":"small-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/21992/medium_square_2431_Four_Cheese_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Mixed_Greens___0002_1.jpg","size":"medium-square","type":"main"}},{"image":{"url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/21992/recipe_profile_page_2431_Four_Cheese_Mac_and_Cheese_with_Mixed_Greens___0002_1.jpg","size":"large-rectangle","type":"main"}}],"name":"Four Cheese Mac and Cheese with Mixed Greens","novice_time":null,"portion_count":2,"prep_time":"20-30","pro_time":null,"product_type":{"slug":"subscription","included_in_subscription":true},"protein":35,"public_slug":"four-cheese-mac-n-cheese-with-spring-green-salad","pdf_url":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/public_uploads/recipe/region_schedule/downloadable_recipe_card/12667/recipe_card20170428-4-1sk2zg9.pdf","recipe_id":2431,"type":"regular","servings":2,"short_name":"Four Cheese Mac and Cheese","subtitle":"with Mixed Greens","title":"Four Cheese Mac and Cheese","legal_copy_short":null,"available_for_non_sub":false,"additional_price":"0","cooking_tip":"\u003cp\u003eBe sure to read through the entire recipe before you begin cooking. Trust us—you'll be glad you did!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eUsing your hands will warm the butter slightly, so it combines with the flour more easily. This mixture will thicken the cheese sauce in Step 3, making for the perfect mac and cheese!\u003c/p\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\u003cp\u003eMake sure to keep a careful eye on the milk, whisking constantly after adding butter and flour, to prevent burning.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e","equipment":["10\" large pot","10\" medium high-sided pan","baking sheet"],"id":2431,"ingredients":["unsalted butter","lemon","parsley","panko breadcrumbs","grated Parmesan cheese","flour","fusilli pasta","milk","shredded Cheddar cheese","shredded Fontina cheese","shredded Gruyère cheese","mixed greens","8\" aluminum tin","milk"],"ingredients_full":[{"name":"unsalted butter","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"packet","displayOrder":1,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/265/medium_square_butter-test.jpg"},{"name":"lemon","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":2,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/16/medium_square_LEMON_SLICED_1_copy.jpg"},{"name":"parsley","quantity":"0.125","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":3,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1279/medium_square_medium_square_parsley-test.jpg"},{"name":"panko breadcrumbs","quantity":"0.25","measurementUnit":"cup","displayOrder":4,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/21/medium_square_PANKO_BREADCRUMBS_copy.jpg"},{"name":"grated Parmesan cheese","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":5,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/22/medium_square_parmesan-cheese-2.jpg"},{"name":"flour","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":6,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/285/medium_square_FLOUR_copy.jpg"},{"name":"fusilli pasta","quantity":"8.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":7,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/1957/medium_square_sfoglini_fusili.jpg"},{"name":"milk","quantity":"12.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":8,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/598/medium_square_coconut-milk.jpg"},{"name":"shredded Cheddar cheese","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":9,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/20/medium_square_shredded-cheddar.jpg"},{"name":"shredded Fontina cheese","quantity":"2.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":10,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/423/medium_square_shredded-cheese-asiago.jpg"},{"name":"shredded Gruyère cheese","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":11,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/280/medium_square_dairy-gruyere1.jpg"},{"name":"mixed greens","quantity":"3.0","measurementUnit":"ounce","displayOrder":12,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/638/medium_square_veg-springmix.jpg"},{"name":"8\" aluminum tin","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/830/medium_square_square_baking_tin.jpg"},{"name":"milk","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":14,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/129/medium_square_coconut-milk.jpg"}],"is_tastemaker":false,"upgradeable":false,"is_holiday_hack":false,"pantry_items":["olive oil","kosher salt","black pepper"],"pantry_items_full":[{"name":"+ 1 teaspoon olive oil","quantity":"1.0","measurementUnit":"tablespoon","displayOrder":13,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/267/medium_square_olive-oil-test.jpg"},{"name":"kosher salt","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":null,"displayOrder":14,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/473/medium_square_kosher-salt.jpg"},{"name":"black pepper","quantity":null,"measurementUnit":"","displayOrder":15,"imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/recipe/ingredient/image/493/medium_square_spice-black-pepper-test.jpg"}],"steps":[{"title":"Prepare Ingredients and Make Breadcrumb Topping","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/20294/recipe_card_size_1._Prepare_Ingredients.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003ePreheat oven to 450°F. Remove \u003cstrong\u003ebutter\u003c/strong\u003e from refrigerator and place in a small bowl to come to room temperature. Bring a large pot of water to a boil over high heat. Halve \u003cstrong\u003elemon\u003c/strong\u003e. Rinse \u003cstrong\u003eparsley\u003c/strong\u003e, pat dry, and roughly chop leaves, discarding stems. In a separate small bowl, stir \u003cstrong\u003ebreadcrumbs\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eparsley\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003ehalf of Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003e1 teaspoon olive oil \u003c/strong\u003eto combine. Set aside. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Cook Pasta","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/20295/recipe_card_size_2._Cook_Pasta_2.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eAdd \u003cstrong\u003eflour\u003c/strong\u003e to small bowl with butter and, using your fingers, knead together until fully blended to form a smooth paste (see Recipe Tip). Set aside. Season pot of water generously with \u003cstrong\u003esalt\u003c/strong\u003e and stir in \u003cstrong\u003efusilli\u003c/strong\u003e. Cook until very al dente, about 7 minutes, then drain and set aside (your pasta will finish cooking in the oven!). \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Make Sauce","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/20296/recipe_card_size_3._Make_Sauce.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile pasta cooks, in a medium high-sided pan, combine\u003cstrong\u003e 1.5 cups milk\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003e.5 teaspoon salt \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e over medium-high heat. Cook, whisking, until milk comes to a boil. Once boiling, whisk in \u003cstrong\u003ebutter and flour mixture \u003c/strong\u003euntil smooth and fully dissolved, 30 seconds (see Recipe Tip). Reduce heat to medium and whisk until sauce is thickened, 2 minutes. Remove from heat and whisk in\u003cstrong\u003e Cheddar\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eFontina\u003c/strong\u003e, \u003cstrong\u003eGruyère\u003c/strong\u003e, and \u003cstrong\u003eremaining Parmesan\u003c/strong\u003e. \u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Assemble and Bake Mac and Cheese","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/20297/recipe_card_size_4._Assemble_and_Bake.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eStir \u003cstrong\u003ecooked\u003c/strong\u003e \u003cstrong\u003efusilli\u003c/strong\u003e into pan with cheese sauce to fully coat, then transfer \u003cstrong\u003epasta and sauce \u003c/strong\u003eto aluminum tin. Place tin on a baking sheet, then evenly sprinkle \u003cstrong\u003ebreadcrumb topping \u003c/strong\u003eover pasta. Bake \u003cstrong\u003emac and cheese\u003c/strong\u003e until golden brown, 5-7 minutes.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Make Salad","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/20298/recipe_card_size_5._Make_Salad.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eWhile mac and cheese bakes, rinse \u003cstrong\u003emixed greens\u003c/strong\u003e and pat dry. In a large bowl, whisk together \u003cstrong\u003ejuice of .5 lemon \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003e1 tablespoon olive oil\u003c/strong\u003e, and season with \u003cstrong\u003e¼ teaspoon salt \u003c/strong\u003eand \u003cstrong\u003epepper\u003c/strong\u003e as desired. Add\u003cstrong\u003e mixed greens\u003c/strong\u003e to bowl with dressing and toss to coat. Use remaining lemon to brighten a glass of water.\u0026nbsp;\u003c/p\u003e"},{"title":"Plate Four Cheese Mac and Cheese","imageUrl":"//dusyefwqqyfwe.cloudfront.net/uploads/culinary/recipe_image/file/20299/recipe_card_size_6._Plate.jpg","description":"\u003cp\u003eDivide \u003cstrong\u003efour cheese mac and cheese \u003c/strong\u003ebetween serving plates and serve with \u003cstrong\u003emixed greens\u003c/strong\u003e. Dig in!\u003c/p\u003e"}],"tags":{"all":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"quick prep","slug":"quick-prep","hex_color":null}],"allergens":[{"name":"Milk","slug":"milk","hex_color":""},{"name":"Wheat","slug":"wheat","hex_color":""}],"proteins":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"Pasta","slug":"pasta","hex_color":""}],"publicFacing":[{"name":"vegetarian","slug":"vegetarian","hex_color":""},{"name":"quick prep","slug":"quick-prep","hex_color":null}],"feature":[]}}